 is another story the new york times retrieved october     berke richard l october   new hampshire poll finds powell with an edge the new york times retrieved october     clines francis x november   the powell decision the announcement the new york times retrieved october     plissner martin february   ready for obama already the new york times retrieved october     nh us vice president – r primary race our campaigns feb   retrieved august     colin l powell center for public policy retrieved  february    how mccain does it  retrieved    kessler glenn july   powell flies in the face of tradition the secretary of state is least traveled in  years washington post p a   warrick joby april   lacking biolabs trailers carried case for war administration pushed notion of banned iraqi weapons despite evidence to contrary washington post p a   powell secretary colin l february   remarks to the united nations security council new york city us department of state archived from the original on january   retrieved february     lawless jill february   us scholar uncredited in iraq report associated press retrieved june     uk accused of lifting dossier text cnn february     charlie rose charlierosecom retrieved on   miller greg july   flaws cited in powells un speech on iraq los angeles times reprinted by commondreamsorg retrieved february     a b deyoung karen october   falling on his sword colin powells most significant moment turned out to be his lowest washington post retrieved february     colin powell on iraq race and hurricane relief abc news  september   retrieved february     brancaccio david february   iraq prewar intelligence now pbs retrieved february     pincus walter february   support for intelligence plan washington post retrieved february     remarks at the  groundhog job shadow day program secretary colin l powell remarks and question and answer session with students washington dc january   excerpt on  chile coup federation of american scientists fasorg retrieve