ocomblogslaurarozenpowelladvisedagainstafghansurgehtml  ingrid lunden general colin powell joins salesforce board of directors as crm giant zeros in on public sector techcrunch aol retrieved august     a b c colin powells biography from on the issues  deyoung karen february   colin powell shifts stance on dont ask dont tell policy the washington post retrieved february     blumenthal sidney november   colin and the crazies the guardian london retrieved february     sen mccain releases letter from gen colin powell washington post september   httpwwwwashingtonpostcomwpdyncontentgraphicgrhtml  colin powell republican party needs me more than the democratic party needs me thelonelyconservativecom february   retrieved february     see official website aspen ideas festival  conversation with colin powell pdf aspen ideas festival july  retrieved february     a b powell support for obama doesnt mean iraq war wrong cnn october   httpeditioncnncompoliticspowelltranscript  james m klatell powell we are losing in iraq cbs december   httpwwwcbsnewscomstoriesftnmainshtml  powell says iraq surge should have come earlier seattle times july    henry ed august   powell donates to mccain cnn retrieved august     holland steve march   mccain now has to pick a vice presidential nominee boston globe reuters retrieved april     a b powell endorses obama for president republican exsecretary of state calls democrat transformational figure meet the press msnbc and nbc news october   retrieved october     a b meet the press transcript for october   msnbc october   retrieved october     ohlemacher stephen october   colin powell endorses barack obama for president usa today retrieved august     powell on rush limbaugh cnn july   retrieved august     powell airs doubts on obama agenda the washington times july   retrieved september     carrie budoff brown colin powell critical of president obama politico september   httpwwwpoliticocomnewsstorieshtml  video cnn    retrieved october    abc news re